title: SEPT/OCT Move In - 3 Bed, 1 & half bath - deck - 2 car garage
posting_body: ['TOURING:  You must call and our Tenant Scoring sheet to set a tour.', ' (If you have a voucher you must include a photo of that with your Tenant Scoring sheet.)', 'Features:', 'GORGEOUS KITCHEN with open and bright living area with newer appliances.', 'TWO FAMILY ROOMS (one upstairs and one downstairs)', 'DECK off dining area/kitchen', 'LOCATION:', 'Great Savage location, close to Hyvee and other shopping & restaurants, Harriet Bishop Elementary & Eagle Ridge Middle School, parks and freeways.', 'STYLE:', 'Many updates throughout, neutral colors.', ' New Windows in 2020 with new blinds.', 'GARAGE: 2 Car attached', 'Laundry:', 'In Unit', 'Air Conditioning', 'PET FRIENDLY.', ' PET RENT OF $25/MO/PET', 'Rent for 1 year: $1,970/month plus all utilities', 'Utilities per current tenant - yours may vary:  Elect.', '$60-$100, Gas $70-$90, Water/Sewer/garbage: $90', 'Association Dues are paid by Landlord and include snow removal, lawn maintenance', 'Security Deposit with Perfect Background equal to rent.', ' Less than perfect background?', 'Please review our Tenant Scoring Sheet to determine if you will need a higher security deposit.', 'Pets: 2 pet maximum with combined weight of 90 lbs.', '$25/month pet rent each pet.', '$250 Sec.', 'Dep.', 'per pet.', '$5,925 min monthly income.', ' Sec. 8 offsets income requirements on amount county covers.', ' All applicants must fit the tenant acceptance policy regardless of race, age, household composition, etc.  We will email you the policy after your initial call.', 'FAIR HOUSING LANDLORD']
